schools.name: Rim Of The World Senior High School

data.description: Tired of the busy city life, we have the perfect retreat for you!! Very nice and cozy cabin/SFR located minutes from Lake Arrowhead. Property was fully updated less than two years ago. Features living room, kitchen and restroom downstairs, upstairs you will find a beautiful loft styled bedroom with a beautiful view of the forest.  A must see to appreciate.
